# HR Analytics Dashboard

## Overview
This project analyzes employee data to understand attrition trends and workforce insights.

## Key Metrics
- Total Employees
- Attrition Count
- Attrition Rate
- Average Salary
- Average Age

## Insights
- Higher attrition observed in younger employees (18–25)
- Research & Development department shows highest attrition
- Certain job roles have higher employee turnover

## Tools Used
- Power BI
- DAX
- Data Visualization
